      "scene_id": "scene_01",
      "start_sec": 0.0,
      "duration": 2.74,
      "text": "脳の90%が\n使われていない\nというのは嘘",
      "type": "main_title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "001",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_02",
      "start_sec": 2.74,
      "duration": 3.33,
      "text": "“脳の10%しか\n使っていない”\nは科学的に誤り",
      "type": "title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_03",
      "start_sec": 6.07,
      "duration": 3.59,
      "text": "現代の脳画像技術（fMRIなど）では、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_04",
      "start_sec": 9.66,
      "duration": 2.18,
      "text": "脳はほぼ常に全域で活動しており、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "002",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_05",
      "start_sec": 11.84,
      "duration": 2.04,
      "text": "使われていない領域など存在しない。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_06",
      "start_sec": 13.88,
      "duration": 1.69,
      "text": "安静時ですら複数の部位が",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_07",
      "start_sec": 15.56,
      "duration": 3.04,
      "text": "同時に働いており、「10%説」は",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "003",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_08",
      "start_sec": 18.6,
      "duration": 2.09,
      "text": "科学的に完全な誤情報とされている。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "004",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_09",
      "start_sec": 20.69,
      "duration": 3.41,
      "text": "“10%説”の出所は\n20世紀初頭の誤読",
      "type": "title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_10",
      "start_sec": 24.11,
      "duration": 2.23,
      "text": "ウィリアム・ジェームズら心理学者が",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_11",
      "start_sec": 26.34,
      "duration": 2.82,
      "text": "「人間は持てる潜在能力の一部しか使っていない」",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "005",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_12",
      "start_sec": 29.15,
      "duration": 1.1,
      "text": "と語った発言が、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "006",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_13",
      "start_sec": 30.25,
      "duration": 2.69,
      "text": "“脳の10%しか使われていない”という",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "006",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_14",
      "start_sec": 32.94,
      "duration": 2.09,
      "text": "物理的誤解に変換されて広まった。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "006",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_15",
      "start_sec": 35.03,
      "duration": 2.37,
      "text": "原文には数値も科学的根拠もなかった。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "007",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_16",
      "start_sec": 37.4,
      "duration": 3.3,
      "text": "NASAが“10%説”を\n支持した\nというのも嘘",
      "type": "title",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "008",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_17",
      "start_sec": 40.69,
      "duration": 3.03,
      "text": "都市伝説の中には「NASAが言っていた」とされる",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "008",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_18",
      "start_sec": 43.72,
      "duration": 1.66,
      "text": "出典不明の引用があるが、",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "008",
      "emotion": "emotion: 驚き (surprise)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_19",
      "start_sec": 45.39,
      "duration": 1.81,
      "text": "NASAはこれを公式に否定している。",
      "type": "summary",
      "tags": [],
      "parent_scene_id": "009",
      "emotion": "emotion: 無感情・中立 (neutral)"
    },
    {
      "scene_id": "scene_20",
      "start_sec": 47.2,
      "duration": 3.91,
      "text": "実際には“10%説”に関する研究も声明も",
